{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}]}],"name":"annotation"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"removeAnnotation:","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1820","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"role":"symbol"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotation:":{"title":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:"}}}